metadata.name: Vulva
metadata.description:
"You can never be wrong when making a portrait; you’re inventing someone that already exists."

A physical print is linked to this NFT. 50 x 89 cm full aluminum print expertly crafted by Solid NFT in Paris, France. This exclusive print was unveiled for the first time during « The Portrait at the Dawn of Web3, Reinventing a Genre », an exhibition curated and produced by 1703.
